                    <div class="col-6 mt-4">
                        <div class="about-image" style="height: 300px;">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1515162816999-a0c47dc192f7?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Team">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-6">
                        <div class="about-image" style="height: 300px;">
                            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573164713988-8665fc963095?auto=format&fit=crop&w=600&q=80" alt="Meeting">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 ps-lg-5" data-aos="fade-left">
                <h2 class="fw-bold fs-1 mb-4 about-title" id="aboutTitle">We create digital solutions designed for your success.</h2>
                <p class="text-secondary mb-4">
                    We're passionate about innovation and excellence. Our multidisciplinary team works hand in hand with you to build digital products that not only look amazing, but deliver measurable results and a strong return on investment.
                </p>
                <ul class="list-unstyled mb-5">
                    <li class="mb-3 d-flex align-items-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="0">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-primary me-3 fs-6"></i>
                        <span class="text-secondary fw-medium">Customized strategies for your brand</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="mb-3 d-flex align-items-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-primary me-3 fs-6"></i>
                        <span class="text-secondary fw-medium">Ongoing technical support and maintenance</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="mb-3 d-flex align-items-center" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-check text-primary me-3 fs-6"></i>
                        <span class="text-secondary fw-medium">Conversion and ROI-focused approach</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <div class="d-flex align-items-center flex-wrap">
                    <a href="#services" class="btn btn-primary px-4 py-2 me-4 mb-2">KNOW MORE</a>
                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-2">
                        <div class="trophy-icon-wrap text-primary fs-2 me-2"><i class="fa-solid fa-trophy"></i></div>
                        <span class="fw-bold text-primary fs-5"><span class="count-up" data-target="10">0</span>+ Years Experience</span>
